cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.SI, cs.NI 

The paper focuses on analyzing user reviews of IoT devices and their corresponding apps, which suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR) to extract the issues users encountered. The paper also discusses challenges in software development and integration, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and system integration (cs.SI). Finally, the paper deals with networked sensors and actuators, which suggests a focus on networking and internet technologies (cs.NI).
